Revision history for Tree-STR

0.06  20260227
    - The query methods are now compatible with Tree::R,
      i.e. they accept an array ref and add to that if passed.

0.05  20260221
    - Linearise the query methods (no more recursion).
    - Some micro-optimisations.

0.04  20260127
    - Fix URLs in Makefile.PL metadata

0.03  20260124
    - Fix manifest issues.

0.02  20260123
    - Fix some egregious bugs in v0.01.
    - More tests.

0.01  20260123
    - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
    - Probably has bugs.


